metadata.name: NyanCo #0001
metadata.description:
Lord Nyan was born in Japan, as an influencer cat, in NFT Collection.  
Modeled after Hachiko the loyal dog, the symbolic bronze statue of Shibuya, Tokyo in the real world Nyan-ko, the loyal cat, was created as a new symbol of the Web 3.0 virtual Tokyo, Shibuya.
